pros:
Incredibly smart people to work with; 
Fairly easy to move between groups;
Total compensation, if you care to understand it in depth, is great;
If you happen to work on projects with professional, result-oriented, non-political team mates, it is indeed an exciting and great place to work. Such opportunities are sadly getting to be far and few between, of late.

